title: Rs 45,000 for 'safe passage' from Pisochyn to Lviv - Economic Times
content: Rs 45,000 for 'safe passage' from Pisochyn to Lviv  Economic Times
description: "All I can say is that my son is being rescued. I don't mind paying the money, but I can't keep waiting endlessly for the government rescue to happen," an angry parent told ET after his son boarded a bus from Pisochyn. He sent SOS messages to several people seeking help for his 19-year-old son when he was stuck in Kharkiv, but none could help.
